    <item>
      <title>纽约州称特朗普应在上诉前缴纳全额欺诈罚款的保释金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/ny-says-trump-should-post-bond-for-full-fraud-fine-before-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约总检察长对唐纳德·特朗普声称他可能不得不亏本出售房产才能获得这位房地产大亨对 4.54 亿美元民事欺诈罚款提出上诉所需的保证金的说法提出了异议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/ny-says-trump-should-post-bond-for-full-fraud-fine-before-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:54:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被禁止的塞内加尔反对党领袖敦促最高法院取消投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/barred-senegal-opposition-leader-urges-top-court-to-cancel-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔反对派政治家卡里姆·韦德 (Karim Wade) 要求该国最高法院废除将选举安排在 3 月 24 日的决定，理由是没有足够的时间准备投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/barred-senegal-opposition-leader-urges-top-court-to-cancel-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙阻止勒庞和极右翼上台的计划有缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-11/le-plan-imparfait-de-macron-pour-empecher-le-pen-et-l-extreme-droite-d-arriver-au-pouvoir</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 6 月份欧洲选举的民意调查中，玛丽娜·勒庞领先于伊曼纽尔·马克龙。这种热情会带领它在 2027 年取得胜利吗？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-03-11/le-plan-imparfait-de-macron-pour-empecher-le-pen-et-l-extreme-droite-d-arriver-au-pouvoir</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 22:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着加沙死亡人数增加，以色列和美国之间的紧张局势加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/israel-hamas-war-revealing-tension-between-biden-netanyahu-over-gaza-deaths</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几乎每天都打的电话几个月前就停止了。现在，乔·拜登和本杰明·内塔尼亚胡之间因以色列对哈马斯战争而产生的紧张关系随着两位领导人公开争吵而公开化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/israel-hamas-war-revealing-tension-between-biden-netanyahu-over-gaza-deaths</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 21:07:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登表示在波兰提出要求之前无需派遣更多美军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/poland-s-president-will-ask-biden-to-send-more-us-troops-to-protect-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，在波兰国家元首请求提供更多人员和军事装备以缓解对俄罗斯侵略北约东翼的担忧之前，不需要增派美军来加强波兰边境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/poland-s-president-will-ask-biden-to-send-more-us-troops-to-protect-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 21:03:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国间谍警告称乌克兰战争势头转向俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/momentum-shifting-toward-russia-in-ukraine-war-us-spies-warn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国情报机构周一告诉参议员，乌克兰的僵局正在“扭转局势”，对莫斯科有利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/momentum-shifting-toward-russia-in-ukraine-war-us-spies-warn</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 19:56:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求推迟封口费审判以等待裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/trump-asks-for-hush-money-trial-delay-pending-immunity-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普要求推迟纽约州封口费刑事审判，理由是美国最高法院下个月将审理他悬而未决的豁免上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/trump-asks-for-hush-money-trial-delay-pending-immunity-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 17:31:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登寻求80亿美元扩大美国气候军团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/biden-seeks-8-billion-to-expand-american-climate-corps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统的预算提案要求提供资金来培训年轻工人，以防止野火、保护社区免受洪水、安装太阳能系统等。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/biden-seeks-8-billion-to-expand-american-climate-corps</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 16:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前摩根大通银行家成为巴基斯坦新财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/habib-bank-says-ceo-appointed-pakistan-s-new-finance-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦新当选总理谢赫巴兹·谢里夫挑选了一位来自摩根大通银行的前银行家。在一场有争议的选举后，他出任财政部长，以帮助提振现金短缺的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/habib-bank-says-ceo-appointed-pakistan-s-new-finance-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 13:12:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
